-- MOVES-Old Mutual Global Investors names Ian Ormiston fund manager
-- 
-- Mon Oct 06, 2014 01:03PM EDT
-- None



Oct 6 (Reuters) - Asset management company Old Mutual Global Investors (OMGI), a unit of Old Mutual Global, appointed Ian Ormiston fund manager to its newly created European Smaller Companies Fund.

Ormiston will be part of OMGI's UK and European Equities Team and lead the launch and development of the fund. He has spent over 20 years investing in the UK and European markets.